author: @abhijit856
text: slicing import concept. Hope it helps # Must  maintain the direction # [7:4] Here the direction of index is right to left (<-) and by default step index is (1) and direction of step index is left to right hence it doesn't fit  and the o/p is none #[7:4:-1] Here the direction of index is right to left (<-) and  step index is (-1)  also have direction from right  to left. #Hence it will give o/p
